  {
    "id": 38,
    "name_page": "Introduction",
    "mieutangan": "",
    "mieutachitiet": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">With the current and future trend of deep international integration, the quality of social resources is being continually enhanced, playing an extremely significant role in Vietnam’s socio-economic development.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The Vietnam Union of Science and Technology Associations has decided to establish Phuong Nam Institute of Social Resource Development - <strong>“Phuong Nam Institute”</strong> which operates under the license of the Ministry of Science and Technology.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phuong Nam Institute</strong> - with our team of leading scientists and scientific research experts both domestically and internationally, continuously updates the latest trends in the field of Science and Technology, training programs, consulting, providing scientific services and transferring advanced technology to innovate and develop resources for agencies, organizations and enterprises at home and abroad.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:#ffffff\">Guided by the motto&nbsp;“PARTNER&nbsp;TRUST IS THE FOUNDATION OF PHUONG NAM’S STRENGTH”,</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phuong Nam Institute </strong>is not only a hub that connects organizations and scientists at home and abroad, but also a space where learners can share knowledge, experience and promote collaboration with like-minded individuals to explore their full potential and elevate their own careers together.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">HL1711428184</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong>Phuong Nam Institute </strong>focuses on competency and core values, we become a pioneer in performing the following functions and tasks:<br />\r\n<strong>a) Scientific research:</strong> Conducting projects, tasks, initiatives, and scientific programs in the field of social resource development.<br />\r\n<strong>b) Science and technology services:&nbsp;</strong>Consulting, applying and transferring scientific and technological research results; Organizing scientific conferences and workshops; Communicating and disseminating scientific knowledge; Organizing training courses, workshops, and professional training for agencies, organizations, enterprises, and individuals in need; Printing and publishing related documents.<br />\r\n<strong>c) Domestic and international cooperation</strong>: Cooperating with agencies, organizations, businesses and individuals domestic and foreign to carry out the Institute’s functions and tasks in accordance with the provisions of law.</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<table class=\"Table\">\r\n\t<tbody>\r\n\t\t<tr>\r\n\t\t\t<td>\r\n\t\t\t<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">HL1710137297</span></span></span></p>\r\n\t\t\t</td>\r\n\t\t</tr>\r\n\t</tbody>\r\n</table>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:white\">“Providing society with developed resources enhanced to international standards”.</span></strong></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><span style=\"background-color:white\">With the orientation:&nbsp;</span><strong><span style=\"background-color:white\">“Serving by Trusted Values” (Serving by Trusted&nbsp;Values)</span></strong><span style=\"background-color:white\">, Phuong Nam Institute obviously understands the responsibility in ensuring core values, positivity and dedication ​​in all activities of the Institute. </span></span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">HL1711428237</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\"><strong><span style=\"background-color:white\">“</span>Researching scientific subjects, projects and transferring quality technology<span style=\"background-color:white\">”</span></strong>&nbsp;contributes to the development of social resources in the future.</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Create&nbsp;an environment of <strong>\"Training and consulting services for agencies, organizations and businesses<span style=\"background-color:white\">”</span></strong>&nbsp;with professional resources.</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Provide highly qualified scientists, experts, and lecturers from both domestic and international backgrounds, helping learners advance - promote their careers.</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Build a creative, fair and happy workplace among scientists, experts, lecturers, and consultants.</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Provide society with quality resources.</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">HL1711428266</span></span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Creativity</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Professionalism</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Trust</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Equity</span></span></span></li>\r\n\t<li style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"color:#000000\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Transparency</span></span></span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
