  {
    "id": 41,
    "name_page": "Message from Director",
    "mieutangan": "",
    "mieutachitiet": "<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">On behalf of all staff members of <strong>Phuong Nam Institute of Social Resources Development</strong> (abbreviated as <strong>Phuong Nam Institute</strong>), I would like to send my heartfelt wishes for health, happiness and success to our Partners and Learners.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Dear our Partners and Learners!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Phuong Nam Institute is a science and technology organization under the Vietnam Union of Science and Technology Associations. The Institute is authorized to operate under the Science and Technology Activities Registration Certificate issued by the Ministry of Science and Technology.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">The mission of the Institute is to gather scientists and experts from both domestic and international backgrounds to conduct research and provide services in the field of advanced technology transfer, aimed at developing social resources and promoting innovation for agencies, organizations, and businesses both in Vietnam and abroad.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Together with the professional Scientific Advisory Board, team of staff, lecturers, and experts with specialized experience in various fields, Phuong Nam Institute is committed to furnishing our partners with quality subjects, projects, and scientific programs. Additionally, our specialized training programs will empower our partners and learners with valuable skills and knowledge to advance their careers.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">As the Director, I pledge that Phuong Nam Institute will accompany our partners and learners and deliver even better results in the future.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\"><span style=\"font-size:16px\"><span style=\"font-family:Times New Roman,Times,serif\">Sincerely!</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p style=\"text-align:justify\">&nbsp;</p>\r\n",
